ISLAMABAD, Feb 28 (APP):Prime Minister Imran Khan is scheduled to address the nation today evening and take the countrymen into confidence on a host of national and international issues, said Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain on Monday.
In a tweet, Fawad said the prime minister would take the nation into confidence on economic and global challenges following the Russia-Ukraine conflict.
